{"id":151215,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/你这么搞特权要是共产党来了怎么办/","date":"2011-05-10T01:28:06Z","modified":"2011-05-10T01:28:06Z","title":"你这么搞特权要是共产党来了怎么办","content":"<blockquote><p>关于这种特供即特权制度有很多政治笑话，最有讽刺意味的段子，是苏共总书记勃列日涅夫的妈担忧地说，你这么搞特权要是共产党来了怎么办？毫无疑问，这种财富分配和生活方式上的一国两制，最大的社会危害，一是使统治者脱离人民群众，二是使官民离心离德。</p>\n<p>——时评作者鄢烈山评特供制度</p></blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"lightbox[27605]\" href=\"http://zazazi.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/%E9%84%A2%E7%83%88%E5%B1%B1%E8%AF%84%E7%89%B9%E4%BE%9B%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6.jpg\"><img title=\"鄢烈山评特供制度\" src=\"http://zazazi.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/%E9%84%A2%E7%83%88%E5%B1%B1%E8%AF%84%E7%89%B9%E4%BE%9B%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"325\" height=\"325\" /></a></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\"><strong>编辑推荐</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\"><a title=\"领导的车在北京站怕碰到人民群众不时拉响警报器 特权车辆特爱人民\" href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2010%2F08%2F7135.html&amp;from=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2011%2F05%2F27605.html\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/site_images/2011/04/23/6283541.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"96px\" height=\"96px\" /><br />\n领导的车在北京站怕碰到人民群众不时拉响警报器 特权车辆特爱人民<br />\n</a></td>\n<td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\"><a title=\"男朋友看到我做的菜 一下子什么欲望都没了\" href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2010%2F11%2F13376.html&amp;from=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2011%2F05%2F27605.html\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/images/blogWidget/wordpress_default.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"96px\" height=\"96px\" /><br />\n男朋友看到我做的菜 一下子什么欲望都没了<br />\n</a></td>\n<td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\"><a title=\"艺术人生特别节目：音乐之声40年之后重聚首\" href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2010%2F09%2F9083.html&amp;from=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2011%2F05%2F27605.html\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/site_images/2011/04/23/6295989.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"96px